<![CDATA[<p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font color="#999999" face="arial">Hi {!Account.FirstName}</font><span style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">,</span></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font color="#999999"><br></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.15; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" color="#999999">It has been a couple of days since you visited us at the Toronto International Boat Show and spoke to&nbsp;</font></span><font color="#999999" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 20.4444446563721px; white-space: pre-wrap;">{!Opportunity.OwnerFirstName}</span></font><span style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.15; white-space: pre-wrap;">. &nbsp;Our interest in getting you on the water hasn't diminished one bit. &nbsp;You will find we are just as persistent in providing service after you take ownership and ensuring your complete satisfaction, as your memory maker is working with you on selecting the right boat to create your memories.</span></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.15;"><font color="#999999"><br></font></span></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.15;"><font color="#999999">I would like to ask a favour. &nbsp;Present <u><b>me</b></u> with a challenge that I would need to overcome to get you on the water. &nbsp;It can be anything: &nbsp;trade-in value, price, terms, or perhaps a different boat than you were first considering. &nbsp;</font></span></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" color="#999999"><br><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"></span></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" color="#999999">Give me the chance, and I'll ensure you are happy with your decision.</font></span></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font color="#999999"><br></font></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font color="#999999">Best Regards,</font></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font color="#999999"><br></font></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font color="#999999"><br></font></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 16px;"><font color="#999999">Brad MacArthur&nbsp;</font></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font size="2" color="#999999">Sales and Operations Manager&nbsp;</font></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font size="2" color="#999999"><br></font></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font size="2" color="#999999"><a href="mailto:bmacarthur@legendboats.com" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204);">bmacarthur@legendboats.com</a>&nbsp;</font></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font size="2" color="#999999"><a href="tel:%28705%29%20431-6922" value="+17054316922" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204);">(705) 431-6922</a>&nbsp;</font></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font size="2" color="#999999"><a href="http://legendboats.com/" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204);">le